Minecraft Server Control Script
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The original code was posted with the following license:

--START QUOTE--
License
Consider this code to be in the public domain.  If you have any recommendations or 
make some useful changes, post a reply in this thread to keep this script evolving.
--END QUOTE--

The relevant thread:
http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/121830-multi-world-linux-minecraft-server-control-script/

All of the authors and contributors wish to encourage the continued evolution of this 
script package, and thus continue to offer it in the public domain in the hope that it
will become the de facto standard for simple, free, open-source Minecraft server 
management.
